<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/a-sympathetic-thorn-in-the-side-of-the-bookburners">A Sympathetic Thorn in the Side of the Bookburners</a></strong> by <em>stop1010</em></li>
<li><strong><a href="/halfway-lost">Halfway Lost</a></strong> by <em>Greyve</em>, <em>JakdragonX</em>, and <em>Hexick</em></li>
<li><strong><a href="/in-the-dark">In The Dark</a></strong> by <em>Greyve</em></li>
